Update":"0","version":"5.0.1","dateRange":30,"id":null,"email":null,"key":null,"viewId":null,"cache_path":null,"rankingSheet":null,"cache_exexpires":10,"pvMeasurementsStartDate":"","old_cacheDate":"","weight_of_tag_relevancy":1,"weight_of_contents_relevancy":1,"startDate":"2023-01-26","endDate":"2023-02-25","gaData":[{"updated":"Sun Oct 24 2021 22:07:43 GMT+0800 (中国标准时间)","title":"Linux下安装Redis","path":"2021/10/24/LinuxInstallRedis/","eyeCatchImage":null,"excerpt":"<p>Linux想必大家都不陌生，我们写得大部分程序最后都会部署到Linux服务器上，下面详细记录在Linux服务器下安装Redis的过程。</p>","date":"2021-10-24T13:51:12.000Z","pv":0,"totalPV":0,"categories":"服务器","tags":["Redis"],"internalLinks":[],"keywords":[],"keywordsLength":0},{"updated":"Sat Sep 11 2021 14:44:10 GMT+0800 (中国标准时间)","title":"axios与ajax区别","path":"2021/09/11/axios/","eyeCatchImage":null,"excerpt":"<p>Axios 是一个基于 promise 的 HTTP 库，可以用在浏览器和 node.js 中</p>","date":"2021-09-11T06:39:05.000Z","pv":0,"totalPV":0,"categories":"计算机","tags":["axios"],"internalLinks":[],"keywords":[],"keywordsLength":0},{"updated":"Tue Jul 06 2021 20:44:00 GMT+0800 (中国标准时间)","title":"Hexo博客搭建","path":"2021/05/18/hexoAgin/","eyeCatchImage":null,"excerpt":"<p>Hexo是一套快速、简洁且高效的博客框架</p>","date":"2021-05-18T07:58:02.000Z","pv":0,"totalPV":0,"categories":"","tags":["hexo"],"internalLinks":[],"keywords":[],"keywordsLength":0},{"updated":"Sat Aug 07 2021 22:13:15 GMT+0800 (中国标准时间)","title":"Centos7.X安装Jdk","path":"2021/06/07/centos-java-jdk/","eyeCatchImage":null,"excerpt":"<p>JDK是 Java 语言的软件开发工具包，主要用于移动设备、嵌入式设备上的java应用程序。JDK是整个java开发的核心，它包含了JAVA的运行环境（JVM+Java系统类库）和JAVA工具。</p>","date":"2021-06-07T13:02:48.000Z","pv":0,"totalPV":0,"categories":"计算机","tags":["centos"],"internalLinks":[],"keywords":[],"keywordsLength":0},{"updated":"Wed Jul 07 2021 21:33:07 GMT+0800 (中国标准时间)","title":"Spring MVC中各层次关系","path":"2021/07/07/java-springmvc/","eyeCatchImage":null,"excerpt":"<p>Spring MVC属于SpringFrameWork的后续产品， Spring 提供的一个基于 MVC 设计模式的轻量级 Web 开发框架，本质上相当于 Servlet，是后端开发人员必须掌握的一种模式，以下是我对各层次之间的理解。</p>","date":"2021-07-07T13:25:10.000Z","pv":0,"totalPV":0,"categories":"后端","tags":["java"],"internalLinks":[],"keywords":[],"keywordsLength":0},{"updated":"Wed Jul 07 2021 21:55:52 GMT+0800 (中国标准时间)","title":"初识微服务组件","path":"2021/07/07/java-springcloud-1/","eyeCatchImage":null,"excerpt":"<p>何为微服务？微服务是一种用于构建应用的架构方案。微服务架构有别于更为传统的单体式方案，可将应用拆分成多个核心功能。每个功能都被称为一项服务，可以单独构建和部署，这意味着各项服务在工作（和出现故障）时不会相互影响。</p>","date":"2021-07-07T13:48:49.000Z","pv":0,"totalPV":0,"categories":"后端","tags":["微服务"],"internalLinks":[],"keywords":[],"keywordsLength":0},{"updated":"Wed Sep 08 2021 23:58:43 GMT+0800 (中国标准时间)","title":"mybatis级联查询","path":"2021/09/08/mybatis/","eyeCatchImage":null,"excerpt":"<p>要实现级联查询必须以内嵌对象的方式进行关联，而不能仅关联主键，仅关联主键是无法做到级联查询的，但我们在开发中往往采用的就是仅关联主键</p>","date":"2021-09-08T15:55:58.000Z","pv":0,"totalPV":0,"categories":"后端","tags":["Mybatis"],"internalLinks":[],"keywords":[],"keywordsLength":0},{"updated":"Wed Jul 07 2021 21:21:31 GMT+0800 (中国标准时间)","title":"Mybatis常见问题","path":"2021/07/07/java-mybatis-interview/","eyeCatchImage":null,"excerpt":"<p>Mybatis是一个基于Java的持久层框架，在后端开发中起到巨大作用，同时也是面试官最喜欢问的版块之一，下面自己整理了关于Mybatis常见的一些问题</p>","date":"2021-07-07T13:15:42.000Z","pv":0,"totalPV":0,"categories":"后端","tags":["Mybatis"],"internalLinks":[],"keywords":[],"keywordsLength":0},{"updated":"Mon Jul 19 2021 23:55:26 GMT+0800 (中国标准时间)","title":"redis的安装与配置","path":"2021/07/19/redis-insta/","eyeCatchImage":null,"excerpt":"<p>Redis 是完全开源的，遵守 BSD 协议，是一个高性能的 key-value 数据库。</p>","date":"2021-07-19T15:20:20.000Z","pv":0,"totalPV":0,"categories":"数据库","tags":["redis"],"internalLinks":[],"keywords":[],"keywordsLength":0},{"updated":"Fri Sep 10 2021 14:36:14 GMT+0800 (中国标准时间)","title":"SpingIoc浅析","path":"2021/09/10/springioc/","eyeCatchImage":"https://img.ctboke.com//ioc.png","excerpt":"<p>学习过Spring框架的人一定都会听过Spring的IoC(控制反转) 、DI(依赖注入)这两个概念，今天分享网上的一些技术大牛们对Spring框架的IOC的理解以及谈谈我对Spring Ioc的理解。</p>","date":"2021-09-10T06:29:46.000Z","pv":0,"totalPV":0,"categories":"后端","tags":["Spring"],"internalLinks":[],"keywords":[],"keywordsLength":0},{"updated":"Wed Sep 29 2021 11:01:09 GMT+0800 (中国标准时间)","title":"Nginx正反向代理","path":"2021/09/29/nginx/","eyeCatchImage":"https://img.ctboke.com//zx.png","excerpt":"<p>Nginx是一款高性能的Web服务器软件，主要用于提供网上信息浏览服务，为高并发网站的应用场景而设计，可以在Linux、macOS和Windows等操作系统中运行。</p>","date":"2021-09-29T02:49:23.000Z","pv":0,"totalPV":0,"categories":"服务器","tags":["Nginx"],"internalLinks":[],"keywords":[],"keywordsLength":0},{"updated":"Sun Aug 08 2021 22:12:44 GMT+0800 (中国标准时间)","title":"微服务间通信和RestTemplate","path":"2021/08/08/template/","eyeCatchImage":"https://img.ctboke.com//osi.png","excerpt":"<p>各种协议众多，那么在微服务中服务通信该如何进行通信呢？</p>","date":"2021-08-08T14:04:17.000Z","pv":0,"totalPV":0,"categories":"后端","tags":["微服务"],"internalLinks":[],"keywords":[],"keywordsLength":0},{"updated":"Wed Jul 07 2021 21:46:30 GMT+0800 (中国标准时间)","title":"RESTful统一规范口","path":"2021/07/07/restful/","eyeCatchImage":"https://img.ctboke.com//img/restfui.png","excerpt":"<p>RESTFUL是一种网络应用程序的设计风格和开发方式，基于HTTP，可以使用XML格式定义或JSON格式定义。RESTFUL适用于移动互联网厂商作为业务接口的场景，实现第三方OTT调用移动网络资源的功能，动作类型为新增、变更、删除所调用资源。</p>","date":"2021-07-07T13:37:25.000Z","pv":0,"totalPV":0,"categories":"计算机","tags":["restful"],"internalLinks":[],"keywords":[],"keywordsLength":0}],"postPath":["2021/10/24/LinuxInstallRedis/","2021/09/11/axios/","2021/05/18/hexoAgin/","2021/06/07/centos-java-jdk/","2021/07/07/java-springmvc/","2021/07/07/java-springcloud-1/","2021/09/08/mybatis/","2021/07/07/java-mybatis-interview/","2021/07/19/redis-insta/","2021/09/10/springioc/","2021/09/29/nginx/","2021/08/08/template/","2021/07/07/restful/"]}},"marked":{"gfm":true,"pedantic":false,"breaks":true,"smartLists":true,"smartypants":true,"modifyAnchors":0,"autolink":true,"mangle":true,"sanitizeUrl":false,"dompurify":false,"headerIds":true,"anchorAlias":false,"lazyload":false,"prependRoot":false,"postAsset":false,"external_link":{"enable":false,"exclude":[],"nofollow":false},"descriptionLists":true},"menu":{"home":"/ || 首页","galleries":"/galler